    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i already checked my INR a few days ago and it was actually a bit high, which means the warfarin is working way too much. if i just replace the warfarin with the garlic and the green smoothies, wont the high vitamin k in the smoothies help balance out the blood thinners so i dont bleed? it seems like a much more logical way to manage it myself than just waiting for my next doctor appointment. what do u think about that balance?",
